35:34.813 --> 35:37.313
♪

35:43.945 --> 35:45.174
Need some help?

35:47.846 --> 35:49.029
I'm all right.

35:55.256 --> 35:56.754
Is this the Wyoming?

36:00.575 --> 36:01.607
Yes.

36:03.083 --> 36:04.907
It's the biggest schooner ever built.

36:06.701 --> 36:07.767
Yes.

36:08.103 --> 36:09.575
How's it get in there?

36:11.272 --> 36:13.064
It's complicated.

36:15.543 --> 36:17.543
I'm Adam.

36:20.918 --> 36:21.997
I'm Hank.

36:22.568 --> 36:24.568
_

36:25.587 --> 36:27.620
[Sighs]

36:33.928 --> 36:34.803
[Telephone beeps]

36:34.872 --> 36:36.952
Woman: You have one new message.

36:36.977 --> 36:37.886
[Beep]

36:38.013 --> 36:39.490
Dr. Kleiner: Good evening, Mr. Asher,

36:39.559 --> 36:41.681
it's Dr. Kleiner
down at the Ashland Clinic.

36:41.750 --> 36:43.149
Just wanted to let you know

36:43.218 --> 36:44.851
that you missed your
hormone injection today.

36:44.920 --> 36:46.586
You don't want to let it go too long...

36:46.655 --> 36:48.154
once the drug's out of your system,

36:48.223 --> 36:49.356
the urges will resurface.

36:49.886 --> 36:51.224
So call anytime to make an appointment.

36:51.293 --> 36:52.425
- We're at 20...
- [Beep]

36:52.494 --> 36:54.728
Woman: Message deleted.

36:55.697 --> 36:57.897
Well, we did it.

36:57.922 --> 37:01.290
[Cheering]

37:01.937 --> 37:05.672
On behalf of my mother
and my entire family,

37:06.144 --> 37:10.110
I want to thank you all
for the kindness, generosity,

37:10.178 --> 37:13.213
and support you've blessed us
with these past few months.

37:13.281 --> 37:14.207
[Cheering]

37:14.276 --> 37:17.741
It has been a long,
hard journey to get here,

37:18.223 --> 37:20.687
but we never would've made it
without you.

37:20.756 --> 37:22.055
[Chuckles]

37:22.124 --> 37:24.824
Now, Governor Elect Warren...

37:24.893 --> 37:26.760
[Applause]

37:26.828 --> 37:28.928
...uh, w-wanted to come out here

37:28.997 --> 37:32.265
and thank each
and every one of you personally.

37:32.830 --> 37:34.934
Unfortunately, in all the excitement,

37:35.003 --> 37:38.004
she completely lost her voice tonight.

37:38.647 --> 37:41.274
[Camera shutters clicking]
My mother is honored
and thrilled

37:41.343 --> 37:45.478
to be elected governor of
this great state of Maine...

37:45.547 --> 37:46.713
[Applause]

37:46.782 --> 37:50.016
...and she will give
her acceptance speech

37:50.085 --> 37:51.684
as soon as she's well.

37:51.753 --> 37:53.653
[Camera shutters clicking]

37:54.206 --> 37:55.734
Thank you.

37:58.360 --> 38:00.360
♪

38:00.429 --> 38:01.628
If he's got a rifle,

38:01.696 --> 38:03.663
tell him to aim for the light switch.

38:03.732 --> 38:04.864
I'm sorry?

38:06.181 --> 38:08.268
The back of the head, top of the neck...

38:09.302 --> 38:10.870
that'll do it the quickest.

38:10.939 --> 38:12.472
He's not gonna hurt you.

38:12.926 --> 38:13.890
Yet.

38:14.896 --> 38:16.541
But you have to do something.

38:18.622 --> 38:19.779
What?

38:24.853 --> 38:26.772
Make them stop looking for you.

38:27.322 --> 38:30.223
♪

39:06.461 --> 39:08.228
Sally: Both a brother and a sister, huh?

39:08.296 --> 39:09.863
Not at the same time.

39:09.931 --> 39:10.864
[Laughs]

39:10.932 --> 39:12.866
Good for you, drawing the line.

39:12.934 --> 39:13.933
Yeah.

39:14.002 --> 39:15.502
Moral code of steel right here.

39:15.570 --> 39:16.503
[Both laugh]

39:16.571 --> 39:17.604
I better close up.

39:17.672 --> 39:19.706
We open ‭at the butt crack of dawn.

39:19.774 --> 39:21.708
Can I ask you something personal?

39:23.765 --> 39:24.811
Sure.

39:25.698 --> 39:28.514
You were talking about regrets before.

39:29.127 --> 39:30.282
Yeah.

39:31.073 --> 39:32.318
What's yours?

39:37.392 --> 39:39.065
I was 17 and stupid

39:39.134 --> 39:41.261
and found a boyfriend even more stupid.

39:41.329 --> 39:42.424
As we do.

39:43.310 --> 39:47.642
And landed myself in jail,
and by the time I got out, um,

39:48.515 --> 39:49.921
I couldn't find my kid.

39:50.338 --> 39:51.484
He was gone.

39:52.307 --> 39:53.740
I had a 2-year-old.

39:53.808 --> 39:56.241
They took him and put him
in the foster system...

39:57.512 --> 39:58.811
and that was it.

39:58.880 --> 40:00.880
♪

40:03.010 --> 40:03.950
Anyway.

40:04.737 --> 40:09.722
You eat like a bird, so food's on me.

40:09.791 --> 40:11.234
It was nice to meet you.

40:11.593 --> 40:12.792
What was his name?

40:14.210 --> 40:15.129
What?

40:16.497 --> 40:18.097
Your little boy.

40:21.703 --> 40:23.001
Ben.

40:32.274 --> 40:34.274
Gus, I'll be there in four hours.

40:34.880 --> 40:36.880
Yeah, it worked. I got the mom.

40:38.360 --> 40:40.360
Some stories you know
the ending to

40:40.380 --> 40:42.380
before they're even written.

40:42.680 --> 40:43.593
Mom.

40:45.076 --> 40:46.396
You okay?

40:47.338 --> 40:48.318
Mom.

40:49.872 --> 40:51.872
This isn't one of them.

